<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CIf you are a mining company and you b=
uild=C2=A0a structurally unsound tailings dam to hold your mine waste, and =
it=C2=A0collapses and kills =E2=80=A6 people, is that securities fraud?=E2=
