<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The thinking is that Amazon can use AMC=E2=80=
=99s nearly 600 theaters across North America, Europe and the Middle East a=
s =E2=80=9Cmarketing weigh stations,=E2=80=9D said one Amazon insider. This=
 would be used for promoting Amazon Prime movies for awards contention, cro=
ss-selling services such as grocery delivery, serving as local distribution=
 hubs, and collecting crucial data from AMC=E2=80=99s annual 200 million mo=
viegoing customers.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It would also throw a lifeline to AMC, the wor=
ld=E2=80=99s largest theater chain whose financials were torpedoed by the C=
OVID pandemic chased by Hollywood=E2=80=99s cut-throat pivot to their own s=
treaming services. The cinema chain =E2=80=93 whose stock traded a year ago=
 at $34 and now languishes at about $4 =E2=80=93 can be scooped up cheaply =
(and without a major premium) for just a few billion dollars.=C2=A0</p>
</blockquote>
