 border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> Spectator profile of=
 Nassim Nicholas Taleb</a>=C2=A0by Rosie Gray, basically painting him as a =
gruff curmudgeon with a heart of gold and a love of Twitter beef:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Taleb described his carefully plan=
ned method for posting. =E2=80=9CWhat people don=E2=80=99t realize is I hav=
e my Twitter fights prepared at least a week in advance,=E2=80=9D he said. =
=E2=80=9CAnd I use that downtime, traffic jam in an Uber or something like =
that, to start executing.=E2=80=9D=C2=A0</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">As well as a good trader:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CPeople don=E2=80=99t real=
ize it, but I openly discuss my failures, my errors and go back and retract=
 stuff,=E2=80=9D Taleb said. The biggest recent example was his reversal on=
 Bitcoin. =E2=80=9CWhen I realized Bitcoin was wrong, I immediately voiced =
it,=E2=80=9D he said. =E2=80=A6=C2=A0=E2=80=9CWith Bitcoin, I had some guil=
t because I made money with Bitcoin initially.=E2=80=9D How much? He won=E2=
=80=99t say, but =E2=80=9Cit=E2=80=99s not insubstantial.=E2=80=9D Taleb ha=
d also been quite public in his enthusiasm for crypto, endorsing a book by =
pro-Bitcoin influencer Saifedean Ammous. So after he changed his mind, he a=
nnounced it in a 2021 paper declaring that the currency=E2=80=99s value was=
 zero. He then made more money shorting it.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But here is his best line:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Taleb had been busy. He had alread=
y published two papers since the new year, on statistical concepts that I a=
sked him to explain to me as if I was five years old, to which he said, =E2=
=80=9Cyou=E2=80=99re not five years old.=E2=80=9D</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">She=E2=80=99s not! That=E2=80=99s the goal, is=
n=E2=80=99t it?=C2=A0Say smart things about complicated topics in a way tha=
t your audience can understand and appreciate,=C2=A0<em>without treating th=
em like children.</em></p>
